  <summary date="2022-01-03T15:23:49Z" status="Introduced in House">Employee Retention Tax Credit Reinstatement Act

This bill provides for a reinstatement of the employee retention tax credit through 2021. The credit was established to compensate employers whose businesses were negatively impacted by the COVID-19 pandemic for wages paid to their employees.</summary>
